            "content_html": "<p>Hi, I'm Alec - I'm a jack-of-all-trades enterprising tech, shoulder to cry on, and guy who generally tries to take most things apart... and sometimes put them back together. <br><br>This blog is (mostly) a space where I can keep a public record of all the hobbies I create, all the people I help, and any fun tidbits I run into in my daily life. </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><br><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/PXL_20260313_192533459.jpg\" alt=\"A Gundam pointing you in the right direction.\" width=\"370\" height=\"278\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-xs.jpg 640w ,file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-sm.jpg 768w ,file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-md.jpg 1024w ,file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-lg.jpg 1366w ,file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-xl.jpg 1600w ,file:///C:/Users/aleck/Documents/Publii/sites/alecs-hobby-shop/input/media/posts/1/responsive/PXL_20260313_192533459-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></figure>      <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #3598db;\">Click here for more cool pics!</span></p>\n<p>You'll also be able to keep up with this blog by saving it in your browser bookmarks.</p>\n<p> </p>",
